  "instructions": [
    "Heat 1 tablespoon peanut oil in a large skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "Add cumin seeds and cook for 1 minute, until fragrant.",
    "Add coriander powder and cook for 1 minute, until fragrant.",
    "Add garlic and ginger and cook for 1 minute, until fragrant.",
    "Add peanut cookies and cook for 2-3 minutes, until lightly charred.",
    "Add heavy cream and stir to combine.",
    "Bring the mixture to a simmer and cook for 5-7 minutes, until thickened.",
    "Season with salt and black pepper to taste.",
    "Serve warm."
